---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-05-20';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Spark & Anvil privacy policy. On-device data only. COPPA compliant under 2026 FTC amendments."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="font-brand font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-anvil mb-2">Privacy</h1>
    <p class="text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
    <div class="bg-spark/20 dark:bg-spark/30 border border-spark/40 dark:border-spark/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
      <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil mb-3">Parent-friendly summary</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed">
        <li>✅ <strong>All apps are free, forever.</strong> No subscriptions, no ads, no in-app purchases, no recurring fees.</li>
        <li>✅ Your kid&apos;s data stays on their device. We don&apos;t have servers collecting it.</li>
        <li>✅ No third-party SDKs in the apps. We use only Apple frameworks plus our own open-source ForgeKit.</li>
        <li>✅ COPPA compliant under the 2026 FTC amendments. Opt-in consent default for anything that would require it.</li>
        <li>✅ Our website uses Plausible (privacy-first, no cookies) for visit counts only.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-2xl text-anvil mb-4 mt-12">Full privacy policy</h2>
    <p class="text-anvil/50 dark:text-warm/50 italic mb-6">
      This is a placeholder for the full legal privacy policy. Will be drafted by counsel
      before public launch, covering: data collected (none from kids; aggregate website
      analytics from adults only), data retention (no kid data retained — there&apos;s nothing to retain),
      third-party services (Plausible analytics on website only), parental consent flows,
      data deletion rights, contact information, and policy update procedures.
    </p>

    <p class="text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed">
      Until the full legal version ships, the parent-friendly summary above accurately describes
      our data practices. For questions: <a href="mailto:privacy@spark-and-anvil.com">privacy@spark-and-anvil.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
